  <TITLE>Clickable hostname to site in name on status page.</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>### ⚠️ Please verify that this feature request has NOT been suggested before. - [X] I checked and didn't find similar feature request ### ️ Feature Request Type UI Feature ### Feature description link to site in Status Page name. ### ✔️ Solution A clickable link in the name of the monitored site ### ❓ Alternatives _No response_ ### Additional Context I would like to be able to click on a name on a monitor to go directly to the webpage, just like the way it works in the Dashboard. By that, i can use the status page as a launcher for all my sites.</DESCRIPTION>
